nique lifestyle each offers. \n<br><br>\nEdgar is also fluent in Spanish, as he is a first-generation Mexican-American, bringing a refreshing cultural dimension to the real estate experience. Whether clients are searching for their dream home or considering selling their property, he brings a professional yet personable approach to every transaction. If you are looking for an agent with passion, drive, and motivation, give Edgar a call today.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5db07bb5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"5db07bb5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Agents Edgar Uribe Sales Associate Contact Edgar Uribe is a dedicated real estate professional committed to serving the vibrant community of Austin, Texas. With over 14 years of experience in the service sector, including roles in local bars, restaurants, and coffee shops, Edgar has honed invaluable skills in customer service and relationship building. This [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"_vp_format_video_url":"","_vp_image_focal_point":[],"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-6363","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/horizonrealty.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/6363","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/horizonrealty.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/horizonrealty.com\/wp-js